ETHICS AND PRIVACY NOTICE:

This tool is designed for ethical UX research. Users of this software must:

1. Obtain informed consent from all participants before recording
2. Clearly explain what data is being collected
3. Respect participant privacy and data protection rights
4. Comply with applicable data protection regulations (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)
5. Securely store and handle all collected data
6. Allow participants to withdraw consent and delete their data
7. Use collected data only for stated research purposes

The software developers are not responsible for misuse of this tool or
violations of privacy laws by users.
